=== apt-sync Benchmarks ===

==== Karmic ====

Below benchmarks are shown for a dist-upgrade from Jaunty to Karmic using apt-sync (see also <nowiki>[[AptSyncInKarmicSpec-JauntyBenchmark|Jaunty upgrade benchmarks]]</nowiki>). The overall statistics are:

* 1259 aptsync files created, with a total size of 9.5MB.
* Total update size is 599.5MB, of which 421.8MB were downloaded (total saving of 30%).
* Out of aptsyncable* files: 416.6MB of which 238.8MB downloaded (total saving of 43%).
* Out of non-aptsyncable* files: 183.0MB of which 183.0MB downloaded (total saving of 0%).

Full log available <nowiki>[[AptSyncInKarmicSpec-Karmic|here]]</nowiki>.

* For a package to be "aptsyncable", there must be a previous version installed on the system and the compression format must be gzip (currently lzma and bzip2 are not supported).
